<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XnaContent>
  <Asset Type="System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[int,GreenTimeGameData.Components.Chat]">
    
    <Item>
      <Key>0</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Hello, neighbor! Your flowers don't look so well, what happened?</line>
        </text>
        <showIf>
          <state>
            <name>puzzle_sprinklers_solved</name>
            <value>0</value>
          </state>
        </showIf>
        <leadsTo>1</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>1</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>I just can't figure it out. I'm constantly watering them.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>2 3 4</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>2</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>You seem to be doing all you can.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>5</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>3</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>It's really hot these days, so they probably need a lot of water.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>8</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>4</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Maybe that is the actual problem?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>7</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>5</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Oh, I hope so. I have to go to work now. Have a nice day!</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>7</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>What do you mean?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>10 11 12</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>8</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>That's why I leave the sprinkler on while I'm at work.</line>
          <line>Maybe things will get better. Have a nice day!</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>10</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Too much water can drown your flowers.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>13</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>11</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>The sprinkler might be defective.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>14</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>12</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>The flowers need rain, not tap water.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>15</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>13</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>You might be right. I'll try turning the sprinkler on for a bit when I come home from work.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>16</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>14</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>It's quite new, so I don't think it would break down so fast.</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>15</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>That can't be it. It hardly rains here so they really need this water.</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>16</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>That should solve it. Also, you won't be using so much water either.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>19</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>19</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>You have a point there. I'll see how it turns out. Thank you!</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>puzzle_sprinklers_solved</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>20</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Hello there! How's it going?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>21</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>
    
    <Item>
      <Key>21</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>My flowers are doing great now. Thanks for the advice!</line>
        </text>
      </Value>
    </Item>
    
  </Asset>
</XnaContent>
